//
// Two fifos in one cyclostatic loop body with different carries (#2463):
// X acquires 3 / releases 1, Y acquires 2 / releases 1. The IRON design in
// test.py declares both; the peel rewrite keeps each producer-side lock
// draining instead of deadlocking.
//
// REQUIRES: ryzen_ai_npu2, peano, xrt_python_bindings
//
// RUN: %run_on_npu2% %python %S/test.py
